  "title": "Insights into deal activity, growth in the private credit market, and more",
  "body": "<html><body><div class=\"node__content\"> <section class=\"detail-page-head full-width-block\"><div class=\"container medium\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-12\"> <small>Antares Capital- <span class=\"field field--name-created field--type-created field--label-hidden\"><time class=\"datetime\" datetime=\"2024-06-25T16:26:13+00:00\" title=\"Tuesday, June 25, 2024 - 16:26\">Tue, 06/25/2024 - 16:26</time></span></small><h1><span class=\"field field--name-title field--type-string field--label-hidden\">Insights into deal activity, growth in the private credit market, and more</span></h1></div></div></div> </section> <section class=\"detail-page additional-height\"><div class=\"container medium\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-8-lg\"><div class=\"feature-image-visability\"><div class=\"field field--name-field-banner field--type-entity-reference field--label-hidden field__item\"><article class=\"media media--type-image media--view-mode-default insurance-library-image\"><div class=\"field field--name-field-media-image field--type-image field--label-visually_hidden\"><div class=\"field__label visually-hidden\">Image</div><div class=\"field__item\"> <img alt=\"Antares\" class=\"lazyload img-fluid\" data-src=\"/sites/default/files/2024-06/Featured-antares-2.jpg\" height=\"381\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"/sites/default/files/2024-06/Featured-antares-2.jpg\" width=\"908\"/></div></div> </article></div></div><div class=\"audio-player\"></div><p><audio controls=\"\" style=\"height:50px;width:100%;\"> <source src=\"/sites/default/files/2024-06/DougCannaliato_v1-3_1.mp3\" type=\"audio/mp3\"> </source></audio></p><p>Listen to Antares’ Co-Head of Originations, Doug Cannaliato, talk about why he’s optimistic about deal activity and the dynamics of the private credit and broadly syndicated markets in the latest edition of Antares’ Private Credit Pulse podcast.</p><p> </p><p><small>Data cited is as of May 2024.</small></p><p><small>Conversations and commentary in the Private Credit Pulse podcast reflect Antares’ beliefs and is for informational purposes only. The topics discussed in the Private Credit Pulse podcast are not provided and should not be deemed to be provided, for purposes of soliciting participation in any investment of any kind, and no Antares party is nor should be deemed to be, sponsoring, participating in, or solicitating any investment of any kind. The discussions contained in the Private Credit Pulse podcast may contain information concerning economic trends, performance, and market analysis, and such information may be based on or derived from information provided by independent third-party sources. Antares believes that such information is accurate and that the sources from which it has been obtained are reliable; however, none of Antares nor any of its affiliates or agents can guarantee the accuracy of such information and they have not independently verified and are not responsible for any inaccuracies, omissions, and dated information contained in such third-party information or the criteria and assumptions on which such information is based. Certain information regarding market analysis and conclusions could be based upon opinions, criteria, or assumptions (including those of Antares) that Antares considers reasonable. Such market analysis and conclusions represent the subjective views or beliefs of Antares.</small></p><div class=\"avalible-pods\"><div class=\"block block-block-content block-block-content9a03abe3-6e62-4857-9ccf-a8978d7294f7\" id=\"block-podcastisavailableon\"><div class=\"field field--name-field-link-with-image field--type-entity-reference-revisions field--label-hidden field__items\"><div class=\"field__item\"><h3>The InsuranceAUM.com podcast is available on</h3><div class=\"btns-wrapper\"> <a aria-label=\"extrerbal-link\" href=\"https://open.spotify.com/show/6WIbsYrL1BXuJMPsZXSk8R\" target=\"_blank\"> <img alt=\"\" height=\"52px\" src=\"/sites/default/files/2023-08/btn2.png\" width=\"200p